<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nexus AI | Master Command Console</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --nexus-cyan: #00ffcc;
            --nexus-gold: #ffcc00;
            --nexus-red: #ff4444;
            --bg-dark: #020202;
            --card-bg: #0d1117;
        }
        body { 
            background: var(--bg-dark); 
            color: #ffffff; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        /* High-End Header */
        .master-header {
            border: 2px solid var(--nexus-cyan);
            background: rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.05);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.2);
        }
        .master-header h1 { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 35px; 
            letter-spacing: 8px; 
            color: var(--nexus-cyan);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.5);
        }
        .founder { color: var(--nexus-gold); font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 18px; }

        /* Security Status Bar */
        .security-panel {
            background: #1a0000;
            border: 1px solid var(--nexus-red);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .status-blink { color: #00ff00; animation: blink 1.5s infinite; }
        @keyframes blink { 0% {opacity: 1;} 50% {opacity: 0.3;} 100% {opacity: 1;} }

        /* Main Feature Grid */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        /* Large Feature Card */
        .feature-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 25px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .feature-card:hover { border-color: var(--nexus-cyan); transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .feature-card h3 { color: var(--nexus-cyan); margin-top: 0; font-size: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .feature-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; }
        
        .badge {
            background: var(--nexus-gold);
            color: #000;
            font-size: 10px;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            float: right;
        }

        /* 21 Engines Special Section */
        .engine-section {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1117 0%, #161b22 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--nexus-gold);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .engine-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; margin-top: 15px; }
        .engine-item { background: #000; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #222; color: var(--nexus-cyan); }

        /* Performance Metrics */
        .metrics {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #001a14;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--nexus-cyan);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="master-header">
    <h1>NEXUS AI</h1>
    <div class="founder">SYSTEM FOUNDER: WAJID ALI</div>
    <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">Powered by The Soul Spectrum Intelligence</div>
</div>

<div class="security-panel">
    <span>🛡 MASTER BYPASS: <span class="status-blink">ACTIVE</span></span>
    <span>🔐 SECURE CLOUD: CONNECTED</span>
    <span>🔥 ZERO-HEAT LOGIC: ENABLED</span>
</div>

<div class="grid">
    <div class="feature-card" style="border: 2px solid var(--nexus-cyan);">
        <span class="badge">ROOT ACCESS</span>
        <h3>MASTER ADMIN ID CONTROL</h3>
        <p>Nexus AI recognizes Wajid Ali as the root administrator. Is feature ke zariye aap tamam premium limits ko bypass kar sakte hain. System aapke mobile ID ko automatically whitelist karta hai taake aap bagair kisi rukawat ke 4K video rendering aur unlimited AI generations kar sakein.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>SMART THERMAL OPTIMIZATION</h3>
        <p>Ye "Zero-Heat" logic system hai. Jab aap 10-minute se lambi video render karte hain, to AI processor load ko distribute kar deta hai taake aapka mobile garam na ho aur battery health mahfooz rahe. Heavy editing ke liye behtareen algorithm.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>SMART RECOVERY & AUTO-RESUME</h3>
        <p>Agar rendering ke doran internet disconnect ho jaye ya battery khatam hone par phone band ho jaye, to Nexus AI wahi se kaam shuru karega jahan se ruka tha. Aapka 1% data bhi zaya nahi hoga. Smart Resume feature hamesha active rehta hai.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>GLOBAL CDN ACCELERATION</h3>
        <p>Video aur Audio export ki speed ko 5x badhane ke liye hum Global Content Delivery Network (CDN) ka istemal karte hain. Pakistan mein hon ya kisi aur mulk mein, aapki file "Makkhan" speed se save hogi.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>NEXUS SECURE CLOUD VAULT</h3>
        <p>Aapki tamam banayi hui videos aur music tracks Nexus Cloud par mahfooz rehte hain. Agar aap app delete bhi kar dein, to Master ID se login karke apna data wapas hasil kar sakte hain. Security layer bilkul "Iron-Clad" hai.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="engine-section">
        <h3 style="color: var(--nexus-gold); text-align: center; margin: 0;">21 CORE AI ENGINES INTEGRATED</h3>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 13px;">In-depth processing for Video, Audio, and Text automation.</p>
        <div class="engine-list">
            <div class="engine-item">Vision 4K</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Beats Pro</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Lyrics AI</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Auto-Subtitle</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Sidhu Vocal</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Punjabi Flow</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Voice Clone</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Cinematic VFX</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Master Mix</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Rapid Render</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Bass Booster</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Urdu Script</div>
            <div class="engine-item">AI Director</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Color Grade</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Noise Kill</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Auto-Thumbnail</div>
            <div class="engine-item">SEO Tags</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Trend Finder</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Batch Export</div>
            <div class="engine-item">Security Key</div>
            <div class="engine-item">API Bridge</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="metrics">
    <strong>System Report:</strong> Nexus AI is running on v2.0 Architecture. Performance status is 100% Optimized. No lag detected. All Master features are ready for deployment.
</div>

<footer style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; color: #444; font-size: 11px;">
    &copy; 2026 Nexus AI Professional Studio. Developed for Wajid Ali. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
